31
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,600
<i>Salt-of-the-earth type.</i>

32
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:15,520
[GB] <i>Elizabeth was before her time</i>

33
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:21,320
