35
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,240
I miss Elizabeth very much.

36
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,840
[John] <i>Stella cared for Elizabeth Klarer</i>

37
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:35,120
<i>during her final days
