and she had sex in the spaceship.

49
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:26,400
And, oh, she told me the whole story.
I could never ever catch her out.

50
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:29,960
<i>She always stuck to what she believed in,</i>

51
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:33,600
<i>and never wavered off
what she thought was the truth.</i>

52
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,280
[ominous vibrations]

53
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:42,560
David, Elizabeth's son,
is my first cousin.

54
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:48,960
<i>Um, he spent most Christmas holidays
with us on the farm.</i>

55
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:54,760
<i>So, he's a few years younger than myself.</i>

56
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:59,720
<i>As far as Elizabeth's experiences go,</i>

57
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:04,960
<i>I myself have never seen a UFO,
unfortunately. I've never had a sighting,</i>

58
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:09,720
<i>but that doesn't mean to say
that I don't believe her story</i>

59
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:15,800
<i>because, you know, she's attended
conferences in Germany and America.</i>

60
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:19,920
<i>She's addressed conferences
all over the world.</i>

61
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:31,720
[David] <i>Yes, she was very intelligent.</i>

62
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,440
<i>I sometimes wish I had her intelligence.</i>

63
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:38,160
<i>But she was widely read,
she read a lot of books.</i>

64
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:42,640
