70
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:11,640
<i>which does not include Akon or his people.</i>

71
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,360
[David] <i>My mother was an amazing woman.</i>

72
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,920
<i>She was
full of love, gentleness. Peaceful.</i>

73
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,920
<i>She was very concerned
