76
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:31,640
[John]<i>Marina McKenzie is married to GB McKenzie.</i>

77
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:35,000
<i>Such a sweetheart and a retired nurse.</i>

78
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:38,320
[Marina] <i>It would seem that Elizabeth,
from the time she was a small girl,</i>

79
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:43,360
