and more in touch with life out there.

80
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:47,880
And... naturally, he'd choose somebody
like that. He wouldn't have chosen me.

81
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:52,520
<i>The first time I met her
was watching GB playing hockey.</i>

82
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:56,800
<i>And I'd met this aunt
