87
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:16,320
<i>and people just warmed towards her.</i>

88
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:19,640
<i>She had that power, that sort of aura,
I suppose you could call it.</i>

89
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:22,640
And I think she attracted men
from far and wide.

90
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:26,960
[chuckles] Dare we say it?
Really far and wide.

91
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:31,360
She must've been very brave
to go off into an alien craft...

92
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,920
and face the unknown.

93
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:38,520
GB has a cousin, yes.
I have a cousin-in-law.

94
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:42,440
He tells... He very proudly tells people
that he has a cousin in space.

95
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:46,640
Potentially, I have a full cousin...

96
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:50,760
