118
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,040
[John] <i>Hayley and Greg Muirhead</i>

119
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:31,160
<i>actually own the farm
which hosts the Flying Saucer Hill.</i>

120
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:36,960
<i>But as busy farmers, they tend to focus
