148
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:40,160
I went to the mountaintop.

149
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:44,560
And there, as I topped
the northern ridge of the dip,

150
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:49,040
I saw the starship landed in the dip,

151
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:53,160
and she was landed flat on the ground.

152
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:57,280
And standing beside her was a tall man.

153
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:02,320
I never hesitated. I ran straight to him

154
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:07,840
and I held out both my hands to him,
and he took them saying,

155
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:10,760
"You're not afraid this time."

156
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:14,720
I couldn't say anything,
I just shook my head.

157
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:17,880
I was out of breath, I was so excited.

158
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:21,040
And then everything happened at once.

159
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:26,800
He just picked me up like a feather
and stepped onto the hull of his ship...

160
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:29,760
and in through the open doors.

161
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:33,840
[Helene] <i>We went up the mountain one day,
just for another talk,</i>

162
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:36,680
<i>and she explained that this
was the mountain where she met Akon.</i>

163
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:42,080
<i>And Elizabeth started shaking,
and she was very excited.</i>

164
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:46,520
<i>She said,
"This is where Akon landed the spaceship."</i>

165
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:53,000
<i>And then I looked down, and it was
the eeriest experience of my life</i>

166
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:59,840
because in the hollow, it wasn't just
