planting those plants.

172
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:21,480
<i>And she looked at that,
and she said to me,</i>

173
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:25,760
<i>"He promised me,
that he would leave a mark for me,</i>

174
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:28,720
<i>and this is the mark
