199
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:23,960
<i>written by Elizabeth Klarer,</i>

200
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:27,360
<i>I made an appointment to see her
and spent a day with her</i>

201
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,280
<i>because I thought, "This is up my street."</i>

202
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:32,480
<i>This kind of
anything-different-and-out-of-the-box.</i>

203
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:37,840
One can also wonder why would Akon choose
Elizabeth Klarer of all people on Earth.

204
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:44,120
Why would he choose her to take with him
to his planet and to give him a son?

205
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:47,560
One of the reasons
that she mentioned was...

206
00:15:47,680 --> 00:15:52,800
<i>that she was a descendant
of the Venus tribe on Earth,</i>

207
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,640
<i>the original Venus people.</i>

208
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:58,960
<i>And he wanted to import fresh blood
into his race</i>

209
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:01,720
<i>for the strengthening of their bloodline.</i>

210
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:06,880
[Kitty] <i>It does have a very romantic
aspect to it...</i>

211
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:12,840
when Elizabeth told you that this man
