212
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:17,080
<i>Akon was her soulmate,
and she had dreams of him</i>

213
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,400
<i>long before she met him.</i>

214
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:24,200
[Elizabeth] <i>I knew his name through
telepathic communication...</i>

215
