227
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:15,880
<i>And I speak as a person...</i>

228
00:17:17,280 --> 00:17:21,480
<i>who's traveled and who has...</i>

229
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:28,200
<i>has met people of different nations.
This woman's ears...</i>

