00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:33,000
<i>are not right.</i>

231
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:38,000
<i>Elizabeth Klarer always loved to...</i>

232
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:41,920
to dress her hair in such a way

233
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:48,520
that her ears were given as little
prominence as possible. They were hidden.

234
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:54,240
[John] <i>UbabaVusamazulu,
"Awaken the Heavens", Credo Mutwa.</i>

235
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:58,800
<i>He was a Zulu</i> sangoma<i>,
a traditional healer,</i>

236
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:02,120
<i>and the last High Sanusi
from South Africa.</i>

237
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:07,120
<i>He also had a very special bond
with Elizabeth Klarer.</i>

238
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:10,920
<i>The story goes that during the height
of apartheid in South Africa,</i>

239
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:15,880
<i>they would get arrested by the Apartheid
Police for visiting with each other.</i>

240
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:18,360
[Credo] <i>I will be as brief as possible.</i>

241
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:25,600
<i>The common story that is being bandied
about by Elizabeth Klarer</i>

242
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:29,880
<i>is that she was an Earth woman</i>

243
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:34,240
<i>who was impregnated
