875
01:03:15,160 --> 01:03:19,560
They're millions of years
ahead of us in all ways,

876
01:03:19,680 --> 01:03:26,040
and this... Even to the fact
that they are a natural...

877
01:03:26,920 --> 01:03:28,440
beautiful people...

878
01:03:29,680 --> 01:03:34,840
