896
01:04:44,040 --> 01:04:47,240
[Jonathan] <i>This new book of yours,</i>
The Gravity File,

897
01:04:47,360 --> 01:04:49,400
<i>what's that going to be about?</i>

898
01:04:49,520 --> 01:04:53,640
We're talking of <i>The Gravity File</i>,
the second book of Elizabeth Klarer,

899
01:04:53,760 --> 01:04:58,560
<i>where she went further,
and tried to write down what she learned</i>

900
01:04:58,680 --> 01:05:02,880
<i>from life in the universe,
science underlying the universe.</i>

901
01:05:03,000 --> 01:05:08,400
<i>But she was not the best scientist,
and scientifically trained.</i>

902
01:05:08,520 --> 01:05:13,080
<i>So she tried her best with the information
