904
01:05:17,200 --> 01:05:19,440
<i>to read behind the lines,</i>

905
01:05:20,240 --> 01:05:24,280
<i>and not to trip
over single words or terms.</i>

906
01:05:24,400 --> 01:05:28,040
<i>There's something bigger going on.
