907
01:05:28,160 --> 01:05:31,760
<i>and she tried to capture it
in the second book,</i> The Gravity File.

908
01:05:32,560 --> 01:05:34,960
There's no profound scientific discloser.

909
01:05:35,080 --> 01:05:37,840
He took me out of the starship.

910
01:05:37,960 --> 01:05:41,680
<i>He wore a gravity belt,
buckled it around his waist,</i>

911
01:05:41,800 --> 01:05:43,200
<i>switched it on,</i>

912
01:05:43,320 --> 01:05:48,360
