915
01:05:55,880 --> 01:05:57,680
[TV interviewer]<i>One of the most interesting outcomes</i>

916
01:05:57,800 --> 01:05:59,800
<i>with Elizabeth's contact with Akon,</i>

917
01:05:59,920 --> 01:06:03,680
<i>has been his explanation of the light
power system used in his spaceship.</i>

918
01:06:03,800 --> 01:06:06,800
<i>Elizabeth revealed these details in her
book,</i> Beyond the Light Barrier.

919
01:06:06,920 --> 01:06:09,840
He could disappear instantly

920
01:06:09,960 --> 01:06:15,760
by simply intensifying the field
differentials around his ship

921
01:06:15,880 --> 01:06:21,120
because his ship is powered
by light in different frequencies.

922
01:06:21,240 --> 01:06:25,200
Which are electromagnetism,
electricity, gravity.

923
01:06:26,320 --> 01:06:31,560
We call it electrogravitics
propulsion or power system.

924
01:06:36,680 --> 01:06:39,560
[TV interviewer] <i>And this subsequently
led to her having lengthy discussions</i>

925
01:06:39,680 --> 01:06:42,760
<i>with the Russian, German,
