926
01:06:42,880 --> 01:06:46,280
<i>who were surprised at her intimate
knowledge of the starship's power system.</i>

927
01:06:47,320 --> 01:06:51,240
<i>At the International Congress
of UFOs in Wiesbaden in 1975,</i>

928
01:06:51,360 --> 01:06:53,320
<i>her speech on the secrets of light</i>

929
01:06:53,440 --> 01:06:57,000
<i>was given a standing ovation
by scientists of 22 nations.</i>

930
01:06:57,120 --> 01:06:59,920
I'm convinced that her first book,

931
01:07:00,040 --> 01:07:06,240
the visit with Akon, to Alpha Centauri...
