963
01:09:16,680 --> 01:09:18,600
<i>bypassed me all those years ago.</i>

964
01:09:18,720 --> 01:09:20,680
This is the book that...

965
01:09:21,640 --> 01:09:28,320
had a lot of underlining
and writing in... by Elizabeth.

966
01:09:28,440 --> 01:09:31,480
<i>To me, it was just marking areas...</i>

967
01:09:33,160 --> 01:09:35,560
<i>that were of interest to her for her book.</i>

968
01:09:35,680 --> 01:09:40,440
<i>I couldn't find the exact words,
or strings of words,</i>

969
01:09:40,560 --> 01:09:43,880
<i>or paragraphs in her book,</i>
Beyond the Light Barrier.

970
01:09:44,800 --> 01:09:49,800
<i>It's just highlighting scientific words
