981
01:10:40,120 --> 01:10:43,320
[Paul] <i>I started reading...</i>
Beyond the Light Barrier,

982
01:10:43,440 --> 01:10:45,560
<i>and also reading about her.</i>

983
01:10:45,680 --> 01:10:50,240
And I can't tell you the number of times I
shouted out loud in my quiet little study,

984
01:10:50,360 --> 01:10:53,960
I went, "Wah! Wah! What?!"

985
01:10:54,080 --> 01:10:58,800
<i>A pilot, a painter,
played the piano, rode horses.</i>

986
01:10:58,920 --> 01:11:02,120
<i>"Renaissance woman"
