987
01:11:02,240 --> 01:11:07,240
<i>"Do people realize what this person
was way back in the '50s and stuff?"</i>

988
01:11:07,360 --> 01:11:10,520
It's almost beyond belief,
but she did those things.

989
01:11:10,640 --> 01:11:12,480
I think that's what kept me going

990
01:11:12,600 --> 01:11:17,240
<i>because I had what I call
my 35-year appointment with Klarer.</i>

991
01:11:25,600 --> 01:11:28,480
<i>So, how do you get your message across?
How do you...</i>

992
01:11:28,600 --> 01:11:32,000
<i>Because you know,
subtle things don't get messages across.</i>

993
01:11:32,120 --> 01:11:35,840
<i>The things that get messages across
