it's like connecting with that.

1002
01:12:01,640 --> 01:12:03,600
And Klarer connected with the stillness.

1003
01:12:04,320 --> 01:12:07,680
And in the stillness came... came Akon.

1004
01:12:07,800 --> 01:12:10,480
People might not believe Klarer's story,

1005
01:12:10,880 --> 01:12:15,760
but, I think perhaps, what she did was,
she lied her truth.

1006
01:12:15,880 --> 01:12:21,120
She... she... wanted to get her story
to many, many people,

1007
01:12:21,240 --> 01:12:24,560
and the only way she could do that
was by lying...

1008
01:12:25,720 --> 01:12:26,920
the truth.

